additionalProperty.name: Ingredients
additionalProperty.value: Ingredients: Dairy ingredients (reconstituted skim milk and/or reconstituted buttermilk, butter oil, cream), sugar, cocoa components (9%^)(cocoa butter, cocoa mass), glucose, vegetable oil, emulsifiers (E471, soy lecithin, sunflower lecithin), stabilisers (E412, E410, E407, E401), flavours, malt extract (from barley), sodium bicarbonate, colour (E160b), salt, pea protein, maltodextrin, erythritol, sucralose. Contains milk, soy and gluten containing cereals (barley). May contain wheat, peanuts and tree nuts.
